_sText:
this is the knife form of my new map*(s) called knife_cosecant (pre-calculious students, be very afraid) the aim of this was a really good looking knife map, that would support allot of players and be allot of fun. this map will auto-set the gravity to 375 and sv_airaccelerate to 999 without any help from an admin. thes are the optimal values for the map as it will allow you to get around effectivly.
side notes:
it features HDR and LDR, with proper cubemaps for both, so all you fans of hdr are in for a treat.

special thanks:
sixtoes, for re-sparking my intrest in mapping and beta testing
sloth, for beta testing
ankaril for helping with batch compiler, even though i couldnt use it for this.
and last but not least, VALVe, for providing such a nice new hammer interface, and of corse all their content.
